ingin menghalangi

00:09:47.863 --> 00:09:49.023
jalanmu, tapi takdir membawa

00:09:49.343 --> 00:09:51.943
kita bertatap muka pada
waktu tertentu setiap saat.

00:09:52.143 --> 00:09:53.983
